Submit Your Time Sheet

To submit a time sheet:
Open Service Resources in the App Launcher.
Select a service resource.
Click Related, then scroll to Time Sheets and click New.
Set start and end dates for the time sheet duration.
Select Submitted from the Status dropdown menu.
Save changes.
title: Submitting Time Sheets in Service Cloud
